.name
Empire
.fullname
Amiga Empire
.type
Strategy Game, Multi-Player
.short
Multi-player war game
.description
Amiga Empire is an implementation of the old Peter Langston UNIX Empire
game. It can run stand-alone or from BBS's. Empire is a multi-player
game featuring exploration, economics, land/naval/air/artillery combat,
etc. An old favorite for many. The original version was written by Chris
Gray. '.w' versions are enhancements by David Wright.
